# FPGA Pin Mapping

The design assumes an Intel MAX10 FPGA board.

| FPGA Resource | Connected To |
|---------------|--------------|
| MAX10_CLK1_50 | System clock |
| SW[7:0] | Operand input |
| SW[9:8] | Operation select |
| KEY0 | Latch Operand A |
| KEY1 (Short) | Latch Operand B |
| KEY1 (Long) | Toggle Mode |
| HEX0 | Result[3:0] |
| HEX1 | Result[7:4] |
| HEX2 | Result[11:8] |
| HEX3 | Result[15:12] |
| HEX4 | Operation indicator |
| HEX5 | Mode indicator |

